latestIgtvVideos.title: Duroflex Mattress
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This festive season I decided to gift good sleep to my family by brining home a #Duroflex mattress as a Diwali gift. 
I visited the Duroflex Experience Centre at Banjara Hills to find the right orthopedic mattress from their doctor recommended Duropedic range for my parents.
They followed all the safety protocols and I got really impressed by their wide range of mattresses and the insights provided by them .  
Team Duroflex helped me understand all the features and uses of the mattresses. It became so easy for me to choose the right one in no time. I decided to go for Strength from the Duropedic range because of the health benefits and the fact that it is recommendation by the doctors at National Health Academy (NHA).
I think this is the most thoughtful gift one can ever give.
Thank you @duroflexworld for introducing me to the world of good sleep.
You guys can also visit the store at Banjara Hills, Hyderabad or simply head to duroflexworld.com to find the one nearest you or shop online. They will deliver the selected mattress at your doorstep in no time.
If you shop before Diwali you can get rewards up to Rs. 7000 on your purchase.
#Giftofgoodsleep #Sleepexperts #Madeinindia #DiwaliGifting #hyderabadblogger

latestPosts.caption:
Pochampally Ikkat Pattu ✨

From the heart of Telangana, where every thread tells a story, comes the timeless beauty of Pochampally handlooms 🪡

They weave 3 types of ikkat - Horizontal,Vertical & Double Ikkat 

Each saree, woven over days with love and precision, carries the dreams of artisans who keep our heritage alive ❤️ 

Attached the contact details and location in video,Do support them and be a part of our beautiful story of art 🤗

#supportweavers #indianheritage #pochampallyikkat #handlooms #telanganatourism #unsponsored

Rajanna Siri Pattu ✨
Match Box Saree | Ring Saree | Gold & Silver Silk Saree 

Today’s weaving story takes us to Sircilla, the heart of Telangana’s textile heritage🧵 

I had the chance to meet Hariprasad and his wife, a couple whose dedication and skill shine through their unique creations like matchbox sarees, ring sarees, 2-gram gold and silver sarees, and even custom sarees with woven memories✨ 

Hariprasad got an invitation to Narendra Modi’s Oath taking ceremony as PM and he was so happy about the recognition he is receiving ❣️

It takes up to 30 days to craft just one saree, but what they create is nothing short of timeless art 🪡 
Let’s honor and support India’s rich handloom traditions 🇮🇳 

Attached the contact details at the end of the video,Do support them and be a part of our beautiful story of art 🤗

#HandloomLove #RajannaSiriPattu #WeavingHeritage #SupportArtisans #SircillaSarees #matchboxsaree #supportweavers #indianheritage #handlooms #telanganatourism #Sircilla #unsponsored

Gadwal pattu | Gadwal cotton |

Do you know where the first alankarana pancha for Tirupati Swami Vaaru’s Brahmotsavam comes from? 🙏🏼✨

It’s crafted by the skilled hands of Gadwal weavers in Telangana, taking 40 days of dedication 🕉️

Yet, this ancient craft is at risk, as the next generation drifts away from weaving, and imitation sarees threaten their livelihood 😅

I’ve attached the details of few weavers from gadwal at the end of the video you guys can contact them for sarees 🫶🏼

Let’s save this art before it vanishes. 

Support our weavers and honour India’s heritage 

#GadwalWeavers #SaveOurHeritage #Handlooms #Telanganatourism #Unsponsored 
#Indianheritage #Supportweavers #Gadwalpattu
